osque of the Messenger of Allah, and the Furthest Mosque in Jerusalem.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 1189, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1397 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":36133,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/05\/11\/salat-al-quds\/","url_meta":{"origin":28535,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Jerusalem: Virtue of prayers in Masjid al-Aqsa","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 11, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Darda reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe virtue of prayer in Masjid al-Haram is one hundred thousand times better than prayer elsewhere, prayer in this mosque of mine is one thousand times better than prayer elsewhere, and prayer in Bayt al-Maqdis is better than\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":5635,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/29\/qiblah-al-quds-to-makkah\/","url_meta":{"origin":28535,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Qiblah: Changing direction of prayer from Jerusalem to Mecca","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 29, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, used to pray towards the Sacred House in Jerusalem, then it was revealed to him, \u201cWe have certainly seen you turning your face to the heaven. We will surely turn you to a direction of prayer\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":13038,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/03\/23\/whole-earth-is-a-masjid-mosque\/","url_meta":{"origin":28535,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Prayer: Entire earth place of prayer except graveyards, bathrooms","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 23, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id al-Khudri reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe entire earth has been made a place of prayer,\u00a0except for graveyards and washrooms.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 317 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Ibn Taymiyyah \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0633\u064e\u0639\u0650\u064a\u062f\u064d \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062e\u064f\u062f\u0652\u0631\u0650\u064a\u0650\u0651 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":41153,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/09\/08\/makkah-quds-masjid-aqsa\/","url_meta":{"origin":28535,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Masajid: Mecca, Jerusalem, then earth","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 8, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Dharr reported